title: Bryant McFadden on Le'Veon Bell deal, Richard Sherman ripping Seahawks (Football 07/17)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Bryant McFadden of CBS Sports to break down some of the latest news around the NFL, including Richard Sherman's comments that the Seahawks have "lost their way," whether Le'Veon Bell could sit out the season, his thoughts on the franchise tag and much more, plus a game of Would You Rather.
